An AI Agent that searches the web and summarizes webpages for you.


I am learning to create AI Agents. This is my AI Agent which I have made using ReAct framework. I havem't used any AI Agent framework. This is to learn everthing from the scratch.

You can run this using Gemini API or either running AI model locally.
I have used Gemini for cloud API and Lliama3.1 for local development using Ollama.

To use with Gemini just run:  
1. npm install @google/generative-ai
2. Get GeminiAPI and add in .env file


Tools used in this project:
1. Ollama
2. Tavily
3. Gemini

I learned how can we can stop just using LLMs to generate text. If tools are given to them, it is much more than that.